<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CodeCalm</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css"> <!-- Ensure correct path -->
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>CodeCalm</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container flex">
        <main>
            <div class="questions-container">
                {{#each comments}}
                <div class="comment-box"> <!-- Use comment-box for styling -->
                    <h2>{{this.author}} says:</h2> <!-- Placeholder, adjust as needed -->
                    <p>{{this.text}}</p>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </main>
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <h2>Mental Health Questions To Get You Thinking</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>How are you really feeling today?</li>
                <li>What's something small that made you smile recently?</li>
                <li>Do you feel you're able to manage your stress effectively?</li>
                <li>How well are you sleeping these days?</li>
                <li>Have you talked to someone about your feelings lately?</li>
                <li>What's one thing you wish you could change right now?</li>
                <li>How much time do you dedicate to self-care weekly?</li>
                <li>What are your thoughts on seeking professional help for mental health?</li>
                <li>How do you usually cope with feelings of anxiety or depression?</li>
                <li>What's one positive affirmation you can tell yourself today?</li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
    </div>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/comments">Comments</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <header class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to CodeCalm</h1>
            <p>Your Mental Health Diary</p>
        </header>
        <h1>Share Your Thoughts</h1>
        <form action="/comments/add" method="POST">
            <textarea name="text" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Post Comment</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            &copy; 2024 CodeCalm. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
